SPAN OF A STOCK PROBLEM:
i/p : {12, 14, 15, 7, 15, 17, 5, 12, 10, 13, 20}
o/p :  1    2   3  1  5   6  1  2   1   4    11


1. NAVIE APPROACH:

TIME COMPLEXITY : o(n^2)  ---> BAD TIME COMPLEXITY
SPACE COMPLEXITY : o(1)




2. OPTIMIZED APPROACH FOR SPAN OF A STOCK:

TIME COMPLEXITY : O(n)
SPACE COMPLEXITY : 
    BEST CASE : O(1) , FOR ASCENDING ORDER
    WORST CASE : O(n) , FOR DESCENDING ORDER
